keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map ' Marks.activateGotoMode
map K goBack
map J goForward
map H previousTab
map L nextTab
map < moveTabLeft
map > moveTabRight
map q removeTab
#map g scrollTop
map <space>i focusInput
map <space>u goUp
map <space>U goToRoot
map <space>e Vomnibar.activateEditUrl
map <space>E Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab
map <space>s toggleViewSource
map <space>f LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
searchEngines:
w: http://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
